@startuml
[*] --> Waiting [The system shall keep the rate in a waiting state until the start date arrives.]
Waiting --> Active [The system shall activate the rate once the current date equals or surpasses its start date.]
Active --> Expired [The system shall mark the rate as expired once the finish date is reached.]
Expired --> Removed [The system shall remove or archive the rate after one year from its expiration date.]
@enduml
